=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=carlothecurious>Carlo the Curious</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 88<br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/25/03 8:33 am)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Looking for tips on soloing Geos in WL for 8th Shawl</span><hr size=1> Got mine in various small groups. I did try kiting some at one point, but the pathing is so screwy it's rather too difficult to be worth the bother.<br>
